data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom brick residence is nestled on a tranquil street within a highly sought-after school district. Boasting classic brick exterior and well-maintained landscaping, this home exudes curb appeal.  The interior provides ample storage and closet space, ensuring that your belongings find a place with ease. The spacious bedrooms are flooded with natural light, creating an inviting and cheerful atmosphere throughout the home.  The primary ensuite is a true retreat, featuring a large bathroom with dual walk-in closets and a relaxing garden tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the versatility of this property. The garage has been thoughtfully converted into an additional room, offering endless possibilities – whether you envision it as a spacious bedroom, a functional office, or even a home salon, the choice is yours.  The exterior spaces are equally impressive. A meticulously maintained yard surrounds the property, while the backyard features both a covered and an uncovered patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Additionally, a convenient storage shed and a covered metal parking structure are situated in the backyard, providing ample space for vehicle parking, boat storage, a small RV, or ATV storage.  Recent updates ensure peace of mind, with a fresh coat of paint enhancing the home's appeal. A brand-new roof installed in September 2023 and a recently replaced HVAC system ensure efficiency and comfort year-round. The living room invites cozy evenings by the wood-burning fireplace, while the recently restored flooring in the living room, dining room, and breakfast nook adds a touch of timeless elegance.  Located just blocks away from Hallsville High School, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and serenity. Don't miss your chance to make this well-appointed residence your forever home. Schedule your viewing today!
